title: Swamphead [2011 - USA] indie zombie comedy horror
description:
Swamphead (2011 - USA)

Comedy / Horror

Rabid Child Films Production Company
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2053447/


An ancient relic buried deep at the bottom of a swamp is accidentally disturbed, conjuring the zombified, severed head of of a centuries-old warrior. The killer cranium takes to the air in a unstoppable bloodbath, exacting a chomping, gnawing revenge on anyone in its path. Now, it is up to a group of teenagers to destroy Swamphead . . . . but can they put this case of bad head to rest for good?
